# Testing Requirements

- Every new Rust module must have associated tests
- Tests use fixtures from `tests/fixtures/` — never depend on actual Dota 2 installation
- Windows-specific code must have trait-based abstractions with mock implementations
- Protobuf tests must verify round-trip serialization (serialize -> deserialize -> compare)
- VPK parser tests must verify extraction against known fixture contents
- Frontend tests use Vitest with React Testing Library
- Integration tests go in `tests/` directory at workspace root
